  <brief_title>Improving Cardiac Rehabilitation Session Attendance: A Randomised Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Improving Cardiac Rehabilitation Session Attendance Using the Self-Regulatory Model and Motivational Interviewing: A Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
